revisions.description: Added new multiclass multilink objects. Added new traffic class mapping for multiclasses.juniPppMultiLinkAgentV10 was added.
Updated juniPppLcpGroup and juniPppMlPppGroup to add ignore magic number. Updated juniPppLcpGroup and juniPppMlpppGroup.
Juniper-PPP-MIB: Added new object to the multi-link group.
Juniper-PPP-MIB: Added new objects to the multi-link group.
Juniper-PPP-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added new objects to the multi-link group.
Juniper-PPP-MIB: Added new objects to the LCP and multi-link groups.
Juniper-PPP-MIB: Added new objects to the LCP, IP and multi-link groups.
Created separate capabilities for multi-link PPP.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniPppAgentV1.name: juniPppAgentV1
juniPppAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the PPP component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the PPP component was supported in JUNOSe 2.4 thru 3.2 system
        releases.
